metadata.name: M_DIM_PRIVATE
metadata.comment: Private merchant information from Merchants datamart

FIRST_NAME.name: FIRST_NAME
FIRST_NAME.comment: First name of the merchant, source: Table  - src_payment.merchants.primary_user_id, src_payment.users.personal_detail_id, src_payment.personal_details.first_name

LAST_NAME.name: LAST_NAME
LAST_NAME.comment: Last name of the merchant, source: Table - src_payment.merchants.primary_user_id, src_payment.users.personal_detail_id, src_payment.personal_details.last_name

ADDRESS_LINE_1.name: ADDRESS_LINE_1
ADDRESS_LINE_1.comment: Address of the merchant., source: Table - src_payment.merchants.primary_user_id, src_payment.users.address_detail_id, src_payment.address_details.address_line_1

ADDRESS_LINE_2.name: ADDRESS_LINE_2
ADDRESS_LINE_2.comment: Additional information about the merchant's address (if any), source: Table - src_payment.merchants.primary_user_id, src_payment.users.address_detail_id, src_payment.address_details.address_line_1

CITY.name: CITY
CITY.comment: City where the merchant is from. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.primary_user_id, src_payment.users.address_detail_id, src_payment.address_details.city

REGION_NAME.name: REGION_NAME
REGION_NAME.comment: Region name of the merchant. For example - Sachsen, Bayern, etc.. Not always available. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.primary_user_id, src_payment.users.address_detail_id, src_payment.address_details.region_name

POST_CODE.name: POST_CODE
POST_CODE.comment: Postal code of the merchant's address. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.primary_user_id, src_payment.users.address_detail_id, src_payment.address_details.region_name

COUNTRY.name: COUNTRY
COUNTRY.comment: The country where the merchant is from. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.country_id, src_payment.countries

COUNTRY_ISO.name: COUNTRY_ISO
COUNTRY_ISO.comment: ISO code of the merchant's country. For example - 'DE' for Germany. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.country_id, src_payment.countries

EMAIL.name: EMAIL
EMAIL.comment: Merchant's signup email address. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.primary_user_id, src_payment.users.email

HOME_PHONE.name: HOME_PHONE
HOME_PHONE.comment: Merchant's personal home phone number. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.primary_user_id, src_payment.users.personal_detail_id, src_payment.personal_details.home_phone_number

ADDRESS_PHONE.name: ADDRESS_PHONE
ADDRESS_PHONE.comment: Merchant's personal number specified in the table - src_payment.address_details source: Table - src_payment.merchants.address_detail_id, src_payment.address_details.phone_number

MOBILE_PHONE.name: MOBILE_PHONE
MOBILE_PHONE.comment: Merchant's personal mobile number. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.primary_user_id, src_payment.users.personal_detail_id, src_payment.personal_details.mobile_phone_number

MERCHANT_PHONE.name: MERCHANT_PHONE
MERCHANT_PHONE.comment: Merchant's contact number for reaching. For example, if address_phone is not specified, then home_phone will be considered. COALESCE(business_phone,address_phone,mobile_phone,home_phone)

FIVE9PHONE.name: FIVE9PHONE
FIVE9PHONE.comment: five9 phone number for the merchant. Replace country code by '011' from merchant_phone. For example - equivalent five9 phone number for '+49666666' is 01149666666.

NATIONAL_ID.name: NATIONAL_ID
NATIONAL_ID.comment: National ID number for the merchant. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.primary_user_id, src_payment.users.personal_detail_id, src_payment.personal_details.national_id

WEBSITE.name: WEBSITE
WEBSITE.comment: Merchant's business website address. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.business_detail_id, src_payment.business_details.website

BUSINESS_NAME.name: BUSINESS_NAME
BUSINESS_NAME.comment: Business information of the merchant. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.business_detail_id, src_payment.business_details.business_name

BUSINESS_PHONE.name: BUSINESS_PHONE
BUSINESS_PHONE.comment: Merchant's business phone number. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.business_detail_id, src_payment.business_details.phone_number

BUSINESS_ADDRESS_LINE_1.name: BUSINESS_ADDRESS_LINE_1
BUSINESS_ADDRESS_LINE_1.comment: Merchant's business address details. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.business_detail_id, src_payment.business_details.address_line_1

BUSINESS_ADDRESS_LINE_2.name: BUSINESS_ADDRESS_LINE_2
BUSINESS_ADDRESS_LINE_2.comment: Additional information about the merchant's business address (if any). source: Table - src_payment.merchants.business_detail_id, src_payment.business_details.address_line_2

BUSINESS_CITY.name: BUSINESS_CITY
BUSINESS_CITY.comment: City where the merchant's business takes place. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.address_detail_id, src_payment.address_details.region_name

BUSINESS_POST_CODE.name: BUSINESS_POST_CODE
BUSINESS_POST_CODE.comment: Postal code of the merchant's business address. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.address_detail_id, src_payment.address_details.post_code

BUSINESS_REGION.name: BUSINESS_REGION
BUSINESS_REGION.comment: The region where the merchant's business takes place. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.business_detail_id, src_payment.address_details.region_name

TAX_ID.name: TAX_ID
TAX_ID.comment: Tax Identifier of the merchant. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.business_detail_id, src_payment.business_details.tax_id

VAT_ID.name: VAT_ID
VAT_ID.comment: VAT identifier of the merchant. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.business_detail_id, src_payment.business_details.vat_id

BANK_NAME.name: BANK_NAME
BANK_NAME.comment: Name of the bank that merchant provided. source: Table - src_payment.merchants.id, src_payment.bank_details.national_bank_name

BANK_ACCOUNT_NAME.name: BANK_ACCOUNT_NAME
BANK_ACCOUNT_NAME.comment: Merchant's bank account name. source: Table -  src_payment.merchants.id, src_payment.bank_details.account_name

BANK_NATIONAL_CODE.name: BANK_NATIONAL_CODE
BANK_NATIONAL_CODE.comment: National code of the merchant's bank. source: Table -  src_payment.merchants.id, src_payment.bank_details.national_sort_code

SWIFT.name: SWIFT
SWIFT.comment: Swift Code of the bank. source: Table -  src_payment.merchants.id, src_payment.bank_details.swift
